title: Exported a single contact from my SG Nexus
comment: It all appeared to work OK but the vcf file was only 27KB. I transferred this to Dropbox and from there Imported to Nokia Suite OK, but only a single contact was added :)  That is better than exporting from Google's People app, which Exported a 320KB vcf file, which imported NO contacts.. hmmm
